So, it's one of these weird

00:35:04.520 --> 00:35:09.807
things where time turns out--how
fast time passes turns out to be

00:35:09.807 --> 00:35:13.360
a property of who's doing the
measuring.

00:35:13.360 --> 00:35:16.706
Very strange concept,
and very counterintuitive to

00:35:16.706 --> 00:35:20.141
the way we live our life.
Because we all think--because

00:35:20.141 --> 00:35:22.940
we live in low gravitational
fields at low speeds,

00:35:22.940 --> 00:35:26.650
we think time is an absolute
thing that ticks onward for

00:35:26.650 --> 00:35:32.260
everybody in the same way,
