again, in just the same way that

00:38:29.009 --> 00:38:33.147
the straight line between New
York and Beijing goes over the

00:38:33.147 --> 00:38:36.287
North Pole.
It goes up and comes back down

00:38:36.287 --> 00:38:40.463
again, because space-time is
curved due to the gravity of the

00:38:40.463 --> 00:38:42.965
Earth.
So, something that we perceive

00:38:42.965 --> 00:38:45.278
to be a curved
trajectory--jumping up,

00:38:45.278 --> 00:38:48.780
falling back down--if you
project it into space-time,

00:38:48.780 --> 00:38:53.230
is actually the closest
distance between two events.

00:38:53.230 --> 00:38:56.699
So, there's two alternative
explanations of these things.

00:38:56.699 --> 00:38:59.449
In the situation where you're
